Microsoft recently held its Tech Summit in Cape Town, with developers, partners, and businesses in attendance. The summit included an exhibition floor called the Hub, multiple breakout rooms and labs, and keynote speeches from prominent Microsoft executives. On the exhibition floor, companies such as Axiz and Liquid Telecom showed off their latest offerings, which are integrated with Microsoft’s enterprise and cloud-based services. The event also hosted speakers who outlined the company’s vision for Microsoft 365 and Azure. Speakers included Azure marketing general manager Victoria Brady and Microsoft 365 product manager Kim Kischel. Images of the Microsoft Tech Summit are posted below.                       